 Dear Students,

 Team Vande Mataram cordially invites you for the talk, entitled:



 .Truth about Kashmir: Story of Kashmir and Kashmiri HindusE2





  By Shri Sushil Pandit



                                                       Date  29/09/2016
 (Thursday) | Time  05:00 PM | IC & SR Auditorium


 PFA: Poster for the event

 About the speaker:


 Shri Sushil Pandit is known as the voice of the Kashmiri pandits. He is
 the cofounder of roots in Kashmir, also the

 Publisher of Praznath, a quarterly journal on the culture and identity of
 Kashmir. A graduate (BSc economics) from

 Delhi University and did his masters (M.A. Chinese) from JNU. He worked
 with Indian Express and The Telegraph.

 He also teaches Strategic media planning at Indian Institute of Mass
 Communication and National Institute of Advertising.



 Dhanyawad

 Team Vande mataram




